title: 'England in battle to avoid worst Ashes tour in modern times'
subtitle: Do you feel angry, depressed or a sense of deja vu? Maybe you feel hoodwinked for believing England had a chance of competing in Australia? Overall, it is probably a feeling of profound sadness, says chief cricket reporter Stephan Shemilt.
